-- EU's Rehn: confident of finding way to support Greece
-- 
-- Thu Dec 13, 2012 6:07am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/13/us-eurogroup-eurozone-rehn-idUSBRE8BC0A520121213

 

 BRUSSELS  (Reuters) - Euro zone finance ministers and officials are expected to make a final decision on releasing the next payment of aid to Greece at a meeting in Brussels on Thursday. 
 They are also expected to discuss the financing needs of Cyprus. (Brussels newsroom)